Strategy - Peak Rock Capital - Private Equity















































Approach to Investments

Peak Rock focuses on investing in middle-market situations where speed and certainty are priorities:

• Flexible, tailored capital solutions including equity, debt and hybrid capital structures
• Ability to effectively navigate difficult or time sensitive transactions
• No financing contingencies
• Rapid and transparent closing process

Portfolio Company Value Creation

We partner with management to drive rapid growth and profit improvement through operational and strategic change:

• Provide resources for growth, including add-on acquisitions and facility expansions
• Invest in people, systems and facilities
• Low post-close financial leverage allows maximum flexibility





