July 27, 2017 6:32 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Peak Rock Capital Fund LP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Peak Rock Capital Fund LP specializes in buyouts, middle-market and special situations investments. It seeks to make debt and equity investments. It seeks to invest in sectors including consumer, logistics, business services, healthcare, manufacturing, industrials and media. The fund typically invests between $20 million and $150 million in businesses with revenues of over $50 million and enterprise values between $25 million to $500 million. The fund comprises of Peak Rock Capital Fund LP and Peak Rock Capital Fund A LP.


